  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Bicycle theft inside Vavuniya school in broad daylight",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A bicycle has been stolen from the Vavuniya Saivaprakasa Magalir College Primary School campus.",
        "It has been confirmed through the CCTV video that the person involved in the theft incident which took place yesterday afternoon (18) is a young man.",
        "The bicycle belonging to a non-academic officer parked inside the school premises has been stolen.",
        "The CCTV footage of the said youth who entered the school premises while he was working in the officer's office stole the bicycle.",
        "Following the owner's complaint at the Vavunia Police Station, the police are conducting investigations in this regard."
      ],
